                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8833" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2216</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">980 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山山家，幸福家，快乐家：“家”文化的传承与创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shan Home, Happy Home, Joyful Home: The Inheritance and Innovation of the ‘Home’ Culture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨燕，贺心茹，王安琪，张玉，陈亚静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江山山家食品产业发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化；超家族主义；利益相关者；价值共创；山山家</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">corporate culture; transfamiliness; stakeholders; value co-creation; Shan Home</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营商环境的不断改善使中小企业成为推动经济发展的重要力量，烘焙行业亦是如此。浙江山山家食品产业发展有限公司自2003年成立，从一个作坊式烘焙店逐步发展为金华市烘焙食品行业的领军企业，源于创始人王评女士的共富梦，依托于山山家幸福企业愿景、以“孝、善、感恩”为核心价值观的“家”文化、四大标杆支撑的“家”文化的落地和实践，以及新时代背景下“家”文化的创新。本案例的设计目标在于引导学生掌握企业文化的内涵及相关理论，理解领导者对企业文化建设的作用，以及企业如何与利益相关者价值共创。本案例有助于学员在现实企业中运用和发展相应的理论，并为通过企业文化建设促进共同富裕提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The continuous improvement of the business environment has made small and medium-sized enterprises an important driving force for economic development, and this is also true for the baking industry. Since its establishment in 2003, Zhejiang Shan Home Food Industry Development Co., Ltd. has gradually developed from a workshop-style bakery into a leading enterprise in the baking food industry in Jinhua City, thanks to the common prosperity dream of its founder, Ms. Wang Ping, relying on the corporate vision of Shan Home, the “home” culture with “filial piety, kindness, and gratitude” as its core values, the implementation and practice of the “home” culture supported by four benchmarks, and the innovation of the “home” culture in the context of the new era. The design goal of this case is to guide students to master the connotation and related theories of corporate culture, understand the role of leaders in building corporate culture, and how enterprises can create value with stakeholders. This case helps students to apply and develop corresponding theories in real enterprises and provide reference for promoting common prosperity through corporate culture construction.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学原理》、《社会责任与企业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化的内涵和构成；企业文化矫正模型；“知-信-行”企业文化落地模型；利益相关者；价值共创</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
